### ===========================================
### POSTMAN SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
### ===========================================
### 1. Copy the accessToken from sign-in response
### 2. Set Postman variable: accessToken = your_token_here
### 3. Set Postman variable: refreshToken = your_refresh_token_here
### 4. Use {{accessToken}} in Authorization headers for protected endpoints
